{"tid":1124603,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【復仇者聯盟4】上映當日大量拋售戲飛　賣家原價轉讓止蝕離場","createTime":"2019-04-25T06:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T01:40:28.000Z","uid":41343,"like":376,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"7960c7a1a6dc1c813e8d489e07c3c22fdb95ca59","tid":1124603,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"萬眾期待的《復仇者聯盟4》已經上映，全城都陷入「劇透死全家」的恐慌，所以睇電影要趁早，有不少人想趕頭班車，睇完可以避過劇透的危機。所以有人看中這點，就連戲飛都炒，一張普通2D戲飛曾炒至700元！<br />\n<br />\n不過戲迷要睇電影的方法有很多，未必一定要用助長黃牛的方法。<br />\n<br />\n因此《復仇者聯盟4》上映當日，有很多賣家的賺錢大計不果，導致要低價拋售戲票，不求賺錢，只求放飛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201904/20190425132715_3_222.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201904%2F20190425132715_3_222.JPG&h=f0497ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201904/20190425132712_0_0000.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201904%2F20190425132712_0_0000.JPG&h=5da58c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦有觀眾因為系統出錯、買多飛而要急放，可惜未有人認投。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/207419/復仇者聯盟4-上映當日大量拋售戲飛-賣家原價轉讓止蝕離場/2?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link&amp;preview=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F207419%2F%E5%BE%A9%E4%BB%87%E8%80%85%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F4-%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%A0%E7%95%B6%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE%E6%88%B2%E9%A3%9B-%E8%B3%A3%E5%AE%B6%E5%8E%9F%E5%83%B9%E8%BD%89%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A2%E8%9D%95%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4%2F2%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_content%3Dlink%26preview%3D1&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5Sb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=f19e5010\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/207419/復仇者聯盟4-上映當日大量拋售戲飛-賣家原價轉讓止蝕離場/2?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm